\s1 N…ôgkiarien infamien
\p 
\v 10 K…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn kw…ôn e Aristakas ye kalabus k…®mru min. In ramni-pre huv…ô tuk …ômi…ô. K…®ni Mak, naorahi Banabas, in m…®n ramher-pre k…®n n…ôgkiarien huv…ô kafan k…®mi …ômi…ô. K…®ni k…®mi…ô nakw…ônhav…ôh ta n…ôgkiarien tukun. Tukm…ô rur…ô en k…®mi…ô ik…®n, nakhak…®r mhav…ôn m…®sarha huv…ô tukun.\x - \xo 4:10 \xt Wok 12:12; 13:13; 15:37-39; 2 Tim 4:11 \x*
\v 11 K…®ni Josua Jastas, in m…®n ramher-pre k…®n n…ôgkiarien huv…ô kafan k…®mi …ômi…ô. Ye kw…ôn…ôr…ôus kape n…ôm…ô Isrel, yam…ô m…®ne kashat…ôt…ô ye Yesu, kw…ôr…ô mis…®r a, iris…®r k…®rhasitu irak tuk wok kape rao ye neai. K…®ni kw…ôr…ô mis…®r a, iris…®r k…®rhasitu p…®k irak ye n…®p…®g …ôut…ôn yame ramu…ô ye n…®mraghien kafak.
\p 
\v 12 Kw…ôn e Epafras in k…®mi…ô m…®n k…®rik. In rher-pre m…®n k…®n n…ôgkiarien huv…ô k…®mi …ômi…ô. In yermam…ô k…®rik yame n…®p…®g m-fam ramor wok kape Yesu Kristo, k…®ni ye n…®p…®g m…®fam, in ram…ôhuak t…®m t…®m tuk …ômi…ô. K…®ni in raiyoh Kughen m…ô k…®mi…ô taks…ôrer t…®mt…®m k…®ni mhau…ô mharkun huv…ô nar…®mnar fam yame Kughen rorkeikei.
\v 13 Yak…®rkun n…®ni-pre-yen k…®mi …ômi…ô m…ô kw…ôn e in ramarkut p…®k tuk nasituyen ir…ômi…ô, m…®ne ye narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®sar…ô apa taon mir e Laodisia m…®ne Hierapolis.
\v 14 Kw…ôn e Demas, m…®ne Dokta Luk, yame in k…®taw…ô keikei k…®rik, iriu m…®n kawher-pre k…®n n…ôgkiarien huv…ô k…®mi …ômi…ô.\x - \xo 4:14 \xt Kol 1:7; Flm 23-24 \x*
\p 
\v 15 Yakamher-pre m…®n k…®n kafak n…ôgkiarien huv…ô k…®mi piautaw…ô m…®ne nowintaw…ô apa kw…ônmhaan e Laodisia, m…®ne pian a Nimfa, m…®ne n…ôm…ôhuak m…®fam yam…ô m…®ne kasofug…®n aik…®n.
\p 
\v 16 Taks…ôvheik…®n ta n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e yakamrai-p…ôn mher-pre k…®n k…®mi …ômi…ô, m…®sher-p…ôn k…®n k…®mi nim…ôhuak apa Laodisia m…ô iri…ô m…®n tuks…ôvheik…®n. K…®ni ye norien k…®rikian…ô m…®n, k…®mi…ô takas…ôkeikei m…®s…ôvheik…®n n…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape n…ôm…ô Laodisia.
\p 
\v 17 K…®ni takas…ôkeikei mhani-p…ôn tuk Akipas m…ô in tukram…ôkeikei mor fam wok a yame Yermaru kap…ôtaw…ô r…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn k…®min m…ô tukror.\x - \xo 4:17 \xt Flm 2 \x*
\p 
\v 18 Yo Pol, yakv…ôh pen mamrai n…ôgkiarien e k…®n kwerm…®k, mamni-pre rhuv…ô k…®mi …ômi…ô. P…ôh r…®kimi…ô tukram…ôs…®k m…ô k…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn yo ye kalabus, k…®rkw…ôji yo k…®n jen. P…ôh Kughen tukrasitu ir…ômi…ô k…®ni maut…ô-pre k…®n kafan n…®huv…ôyen ram…ôm…®r tuk …ômi…ô.\x - \xo 4:18 \xt 1 Kor 16:21 \x* 
